data.title: Former Queen Narriman Arrives at the Orly Airport Terminal in Paris With Her Mother Assila Hanem - October 14, 1954
data.meta_description: 14 Oct 1954, Paris, France --- Original caption: Former Queen Narriman arrives at the Orly Airport terminal in Paris after a flight from Cairo which stirred rumors that she plans to divorce husband Adham Nakeeb.  Narriman, divorced from ousted King Farouk of Egypt, was on her way to Geneva, Switzerland, with her mother Assila Sadek (background) and a secretary. --- Image by © Bettmann/CORBIS
